类 Symbol

  • java.lang.Object
    • cn.ficos.Compiler.Gadgets.Symbol.Symbol
  • 直接已知子类:
    FuncSymbol, TypeSymbol, VarSymbol

    public abstract class Symbol
extends java.lang.Object
    This abstract class serves as Value in SymbolTable (which serves as a SymbolTable). There are several extended Symbol type, all of these is intended to record the useful information of a Name.
